arts.ttl: London City Lionesses 1-0 West Ham: Derby win for WSL newcomers
arts.sum: Kosovare Asllani scores London City Lionesses inflict an eighth successive Women's Super League defeat on West Ham.

arts.ttl: Dominant Man Utd come from behind to maintain unbeaten run - Women's Super League round-up
arts.sum: Womens Super League round-up as Manchester United come from behind to claim dominant victory over Everton; Chelsea secure crucial victory in London derby over Tottenham; West Ham lose their sixth WSL game in a row against London City Lionesses

arts.ttl: WSL LIVE: Scores & updates from 6 matches including Aston Villa v Leicester, Chelsea v Spurs, Everton v Man Utd, London City v West Ham, Arsenal v Brighton & Liverpool v Man City
arts.sum: Follow build-up to six Women's Super League games, including Aston Villa v Leicester, Chelsea v Spurs, Everton v Man Utd, London City v West Ham, Arsenal v Brighton & Liverpool v Man City, plus Portsmouth v Southampton from Women's Super League 2 with live text updates and reaction.
